# Vercel
.vercel/
vercel.json
.vercelignore

# Markdown files (Ignore all except doc.md)
*.md
!doc.md
!docs/

# Ignore markdown files inside docs if they shouldn't be uploaded either
# The requirement says "屏蔽所有md（除了doc.md这一个）" (Block all md except doc.md)
# So *.md handles the root, but we should ensure nested md files are also ignored.
**/*.md
!doc.md

# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Node
node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
*.local

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
